  Depending on your project needs team should define a code style to be used 
  across the project. Here is an example:

  %pre<
    %code<
      :preserve
        .selector
          background: #ccc url('image.png') 0 0 no-repeat
          font: 14px 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif
          padding: 0 4px 2px
          z-index: 5
        
        .selector-child
          display: inline-block
          -webkit-transition: all .2s
             -moz-transition: all .2s
              -ms-transition: all .2s
               -o-transition: all .2s
                  transition: all .2s

